data.description: Completely remodeled with all new kitchen cabinets new Quartz countertop, and new SS appliances. New roof, new laminate wood in the living room, new vanities & plumbing fixtures. The unit was updated with central air. Large master bedroom with 2 large closets. Large 17x12 laundry room for more storage. One designated parking and lots of other parking spots. Walking distance to grocery stores and Roosevelt shopping area, minutes to Oak Brook & Yorktown malls.
